      "title": "Two of Guna's disciples were netted in the crocodile stream",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Special Task Force officers have arrested two persons running the drug network of organized crime gang leader Kimbula Ale Guna along with a live grenade, Kerala ganja and heroin.",
        "According to the information received regarding them, a raid was conducted yesterday (28) near Carmel Lane intersection, Palliyawatta, Wattala Police Domain.",
        "06 kg 440 grams of Kerala ganja worth more than 15 lakh rupees, 05 grams 300 mg of heroin and a M67 type grenade made in a foreign country were arrested."
      ],
